translated: Engebeck, Karl, county game warden, Kalmar, b. 1/11/97 in Grava, Värmland. Son of member of parliament Lars Gustaf Larsson and Anna Fredriksson. Married in 1937 to Gunvor Befrits. Children: Lars b. 1938, Anna b. 1940, Karin b. 1941. Studied at Lund University and graduated in 1920, attended forestry school and graduated in 1925. Traveled to Germany for forestry studies in 1922. Employed by Värmland county forestry board from 1925-1930, assistant at Kalmar county forestry board in 1930-1931, deputy county game warden there from 1932-1945, and county game warden at Kalmar county forestry board since 1945. Awarded RVO.
